      [
        "NO"
      ],
      [
        "I pick up my phone and call [Fabian]. The phone doesn’t ring for too long when [he] answers me."
      ],
      [
        "Look at the hour, what do you want? "
      ],
      [
        "[Fabian], what you did today was horrible."
      ],
      [
        "You left me alone, in the dark, and injured… "
      ],
      [
        "And not only today, but before you’ve also been so, so horrible to me."
      ],
      [
        "Do you even care about me?"
      ],
      [
        "Of course I do, but you make it so damn impossible!"
      ],
      [
        " I do all those things so you learn."
      ],
      [
        "learn to not make the stupid and preventable mistakes that you always do!"
      ],
      [
        "Everything that I do is a mistake to you."
      ],
      [
        "You can’t even let me have an injury because that is a mistake in your eyes?"
      ],
      [
        "Well, that’s just having unrealistic expectations."
      ],
      [
        "I want to be me, [Fabian]. I want to be able to have fun without worrying about "
      ],
      [
        "whether what I do is good enough for you or not. "
      ],
      [
        "I can’t do this anymore. We’re over. "
      ],
      [
        "What?!?!?! don’t you dare, listen here you little bi-"
      ],
      [
        " I hang the phone and exhale. That was an intense but necessary call."
      ],
      [
        "I wasn’t about to plead for forgiveness all of my life for things that aren’t my fault. I won’t put up with the abuse."
      ],
      [
        "I close my eyes and focus on my breathing."
      ],
      [
        "This night, and most likely the rest of the nights were going to be peaceful. "
      ]
